<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#4D0000; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Matt可能让你溜了…</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Aklerep_Shadow%2002.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="90px" alt="Aklerep_Shadow%2002.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:right; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#AE0000; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>但我不会。</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Aklerep_Angry.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="90px" alt="Aklerep_Angry.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<hr />
<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<div style="float:right; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#272727; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>你可收集到了足够的数据？</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Atem.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="100px" alt="Atem.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#5B5B5B; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>是的，Atem管理员。</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Matt.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="90px" alt="Matt.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="text-align: right; margin: auto; width: 240px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#5B5B5B; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>文件#01 &lt;MTF Kappa-10&gt;<br />
文件#02 &lt;帽机 .aic&gt;<br />
文件#03 &lt;C_ROM.exe&gt;</p>
<div style="text-align: center; padding: 2px 20px; color: black; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #E0E0E0; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;"><br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/aiad-homescreen/AIAD%20Logo%20Final.png" alt="AIAD%20Logo%20Final.png" class="image" /><br />
<br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/hello-world/18-1.gif" alt="18-1.gif" class="image" /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/hello-world/18-1.gif" alt="18-1.gif" class="image" /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/hello-world/18-1.gif" alt="18-1.gif" class="image" /></div>
<br /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:right; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#272727; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>你可妥当测试帽机的能力程度？</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Atem.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="100px" alt="Atem.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#5B5B5B; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>我观察到他在各方面的表现均超出我们的预期。可以确认他在进化。</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Matt.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="90px" alt="Matt.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#272727; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>很好。</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Atem.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="100px" alt="Atem.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#5B5B5B; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>但我担心我的行动可能引起了一些怀疑。虽然我尽力分散她的注意， Aklerep还是怀疑到有人在妨碍对本事件的调查，并质疑我为何在基础层现身。</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Matt.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="90px" alt="Matt.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#272727; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>不用担心她，Aklerep不会对此多有注意。她现在有新玩具可玩了。</p>
<p>你做的很好。这些AI对我们大有裨益。</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Atem.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="100px" alt="Atem.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#5B5B5B; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>很荣幸做出贡献，先生。</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Matt.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="90px" alt="Matt.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#272727; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>为了WAN。</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Atem.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="100px" alt="Atem.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 300px; text-align: right;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#5B5B5B; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>为麦克斯韦宗。</p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container alignleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/basic-observations/Matt.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="90px" alt="Matt.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
